A '''Stuffed Tauntaun Toy''' was a toy version of a [[Tauntaun/Legends|tauntaun]].

When [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] was visiting [[Allana Djo Solo|Allana]] and [[Tenel Ka Djo|Tenel Ka]] on [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]] to see if they were the sacrifice he had to make for his [[Sith training]], he gave Allana a [[Jacen (stuffed creature)|stuffed]] [[Tauntaun/Legends|tauntaun]]. Allana became attached to the toy upon receiving it and named it "Jacen" so that when she couldn't talk to Jacen she could talk to the toy instead.

